UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 950
1 shall not lapse.
2 (2) Notwithstanding KRS 45.229, fund amounts not expended at the close of a fiscal
3 year shall not lapse but shall be carried forward into the next fiscal year.
4 (3) Moneys deposited in the fund shall be:
5 (a) Used for the purposes set forth in this section; and
6 (b) Distributed as they are received on a rolling basis.
